msgid ""
"The <span class=\"filename\">bookmarks</span> folder corresponds to the "
"<span class=\"guilabel\">[[Browser "
"bookmarks|configure#browser_bookmarks]]</span> persistence feature."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '    - '
